        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nNot saying the Postman request should necessarily be changed. But we should decide about whether it should or whether [1] should be adapted to not expect this top-level dict \"metadata\" (for cluster-provider it's obviously adequate).\n\nAlso, looking at other metadata uses maybe this is also a problem in other resources like composite app? Need to make it all consistent.\n\n[1] https://github.com/onap/multicloud-k8s/blob/39b7d2f8a79f23141301e7b9abf7bf3a0f2e8f21/src/clm/api/clusterhandler.go#L140",
